# Fumadocs Reference

This repo uses **Fumadocs 16** (fumadocs-ui, fumadocs-core) and **fumadocs-mdx 14**.

## When to consult docs

- **First attempt** — proceed normally from repo patterns and `AGENTS.md`.
- **After friction** — the moment a Fumadocs change is corrected, errors, or your plan is not working: **STOP**. Before the next attempt you **MUST** consult the latest Fumadocs docs. Do not guess or iterate blindly.

## How to retrieve docs

Use the latest content only. Prefer indexed docs; fall back to a fresh fetch.

1. **Cursor indexed docs** — search `@Docs` / semantic search for `fumadocs.dev` if available.
2. **Reference repo** — [Fumadocs UI template](https://github.com/fuma-nama/fumadocs-ui-template) and local index at `src/references/fumadocs-ui-template.md`.
3. **Fresh fetch** — when indexed docs are unavailable or insufficient:

   ```bash
   curl -sL https://www.fumadocs.dev/llms-full.txt -o /tmp/fumadocs-llms-full.txt
   rg -n "^# .*<topic>" /tmp/fumadocs-llms-full.txt
   rm -f /tmp/fumadocs-llms-full.txt
   ```

   Grep for the section heading, read only that section. Never commit the dump.

## Repo gotchas (verify against docs)

- Root provider: `fumadocs-ui/provider/next` (not `fumadocs-ui/provider`).
- Docs layout: `fumadocs-ui/layouts/docs` (not `fumadocs-ui/layout`).
- Content source: `defineDocs({ dir: 'content' })` in `source.config.ts`; navigation from `content/meta.json`.
- Production build uses Webpack (`next build --webpack`) for Serwist compatibility.
